    gmp_insight_title: 'Insights from The Buddha',
    gmp_insight_p: 'By basing yourself on wholesome states, you can reside peacefully and joyfully, training day and night. Being a good moral person is not about following rules to please others; it is about creating a life that is conducive to the growth of your own mind.',
    gmp_note_title: 'Foundation Note',
    gmp_note_p: 'A moral life is the ground upon which meditation can flourish. Without morality, the mind is too restless to find true peace.',

    // Breathing Mindfulness Page
    bm_back: 'Back to Home',
